title: I cannot carry to save my dang life
body:
Here's a little look at my match history lol. I was Gold 3 like a week ago, now I'm about to demote from gold. I'm sad because I guess I really am just THAT bad. Every game I get ( I main adc, jinx if you can't tell ), I get a supp who would rather be a carry instead of being supports. Like I don't understand why every other enemy team's support sticks with their adc but mine NEVER does lolllllll . Or I someone gets autofilled and they can't play their role, but decide to mention it after they're like 3/16 . oh jesus save me lol.
